node.text:
Our resident cat mom @brireadsbooks teamed up with @bideawee to bring attention to a very important issue: cat literacy. To help out, you can adopt (and read to) a furry friend of your own by visiting www.bideawee.org. 
Excerpts from: The Giver of Stars by @jojomoyesofficial, Get a Life, Chloe Brown by @taliahibbert and The Family Upstairs by @lisajewelluk. 
Produced by: Natalie Ullman 
Special thanks to: Melissa Treuman & Siobhan Jones 
#bookofthemonth #bideawee #cats #catsofinstagram #adoptacat #adoptdontshop
